room_title: Escape room "The Cuban Missile Experience" by Escape Vint Hill in Warrenton
room_description:
It is October 1962. You take the place of President Kennedy and his Executive Committee in world in crisis. With the threat of war close at hand, danger may be even closer than Cuba...               

The Cuban Missile Experience is a unique new escape room attraction at the historic Inn at Vint Hill. The Cuban Missile Experience is based on historical events and puts participants in the position of President Kennedy and his Executive Committee (EXCOMM) as they stand on the brink of World War III.
